high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the kitchen counter left of the oven
Pick up the orange cup from the counter
Move a couple feet right then turn back to face the microwave above the oven
Heat the cup in the microwave then remove it
Look up at the cabinet above the microwave
Open the left cabinet above the microwave and put the cup in it
anns.task_desc: Put the heated cup in the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the counter by the stove in front of you.
Take the cup from the counter in front of you.
Turn right and face the microwave on top of the stove to your left.
Heat up the cup in the microwave and take it out.
Face the cabinet on top of the microwave in front of you.
Place the cup inside of the cabinet in front of you and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm cup in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the left, walk to the counter to the left of the stove
Pick up the glass that's on the counter
Turn around, walk the cup to the microwave on the left
Open the microwave, place the cup inside, heat the cut for some time, open the microwave and remove the cup
Open the cupboard above the microwave
Place the glass inside the cupboard
anns.task_desc: Microwave a cup prior to putting it away
